## Core Components

### 1. Containerization Strategy

#### Docker Architecture
```yaml
services:
  sg_core:
    image: centos:8
    container_name: sg_core
    command: sleep infinity
    volumes:
      - ./security_data:/etc/sg_shield

Benefits:

Isolation from host system
Consistent environment across platforms
Easy deployment and scaling
Security through containment

2. TRINITY AI System

Maintenance AI
System Diagnostics: Storage, memory, process analysis
Health Monitoring: Real-time system status
Automated Repair: Self-healing capabilities

Optimization AI
Performance Analysis: Resource usage monitoring
Efficiency Enhancement: Automated optimization
Load Balancing: Dynamic resource allocation

Security AI
Threat Detection: Anomaly and pattern recognition
Risk Assessment: Vulnerability analysis
Countermeasure Deployment: Automated response

3. EAGLE EYE Surveillance

Global Threat Intelligence

Real-time threat mapping
Multi-source intelligence aggregation
Predictive threat modeling

Digital Surveillance

Network traffic analysis
System activity monitoring
Behavioral pattern recognition

4. ELEMENTAL Framework


Philosophical Foundation

The 5-element approach provides a holistic security model:

FIRE (Active Response): Immediate threat neutralization
WATER (Adaptive Defense): Dynamic security adjustments
EARTH (Foundation): Core system protection
AIR (Intelligence): Information gathering and analysis
ETHER (Quantum): Advanced protection mechanisms

Technical Specifications

System Requirements

Minimum

Docker Engine 20.10+
2 GB RAM
5 GB storage
macOS 10.14+, Linux Ubuntu 18.04+, or Windows 10+

Recommended

Docker Desktop 4.0+
4 GB RAM
10 GB storage
Multi-core processor

Security Implementation

Container Security

Non-root user execution
Read-only filesystem where possible
Resource limitations
Network isolation

Data Protection

Encrypted volumes
Secure data transmission
Privacy-preserving analytics

Performance Characteristics

Resource Usage

Memory: 100-500 MB typical
CPU: 1-5% average load
Storage: 2-5 GB including container
Network: Minimal external communication

Response Times

Threat Detection: < 1 second
System Scan: 2-5 seconds
Dashboard Load: < 500ms
Command Execution: < 100ms

